There are a number of benefits to the Family and Medical Leave Act beyond preserving your job. These benefits include:
• Ensuring that you have job protection while you are on leave;
• Guaranteeing that you will have health insurance coverage during your leave;
• Allowing you to accrue vacation and sick time while on leave; and
• Giving you the ability to return to your previous position or an equivalent position upon your return from leave.
